nine-inning Division II victory over Savanna. 
</P>
<P>
 * Deborah Goddu, Whittier Christian, went six for six with six RBIs and 
pitched a one-hitter in a 17-0 victory over Huntington Park St. Matthias. 
</P>
<P>
 * Molly Sinclair, Fountain Valley, drove in the winning run in the seventh in 
a 4-3 Division I victory over El Dorado. 
