2,835 +38.8 Total 2,549 3,260 +27.9 April sales 04,10,10,10,10 1993 1994 % 
change New $234,748 $237,990 +1.4 Existing 241,826 237,421 -1.8 Total 240,390 
237,496 -1.2 LOW-END DRAW 
</P>
<P>
