<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA052494-0253 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 044839 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
May 24, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition Correction Appended 
</P>
