<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA052494-0260 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 044846 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
May 24, 1994, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
