<HEADLINE>
<P>
REGIONAL EARNINGS: AMERICAN CYTOGENETICS MOUNTS TURNAROUND 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 American Cytogenetics Inc., a North Hollywood laboratory testing company, 
reported a $16,347 profit for its fiscal year ended Jan. 31. 
</P>
<P>
 In the previous fiscal year, the company lost $908,963. Its annual revenue 
decreased by 7% to $5.28 million in the latest 12 months from $5.7 million in 
revenue a year before. 
</P>
<P>
 American Cytogenetics said its profit turnaround is the result of a two-year 
program that included reducing costs, raising prices, modernizing its 
data-processing system and raising additional investment capital. 
</P>
<P>
 The company specializes in testing for cervical cancer and certain sexually 
transmitted diseases. 
</P>
</TEXT>
